---
---

<section id="download" class="border-t border-border-light py-20 md:py-24">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-h1 text-charcoal">Κατέβασε το Rheo</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-text-secondary">
        Εγκατάσταση σε 1 λεπτό. Δεν χρειάζεται λογαριασμός.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 md:mx-auto md:max-w-3xl">
      <!-- Windows -->
      <a
        href="/api/download?platform=windows"
        class="group flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-border-light bg-white/60 p-5 transition-colors hover:border-gold/30"
      >
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-charcoal/5">
          <svg
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#1A1818"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="8" height="8" rx="1"></rect>
            <rect x="13" y="3" width="8" height="8" rx="1"></rect>
            <rect x="3" y="13" width="8" height="8" rx="1"></rect>
            <rect x="13" y="13" width="8" height="8" rx="1"></rect>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-h3 text-charcoal group-hover:text-gold">Windows</p>
          <p class="text-body-sm text-text-muted">64-bit installer (.exe)</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Android -->
      <a
        href="/api/download?platform=android"
        class="group flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-border-light bg-white/60 p-5 transition-colors hover:border-gold/30"
      >
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-charcoal/5">
          <svg
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#1A1818"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-h3 text-charcoal group-hover:text-gold">Android</p>
          <p class="text-body-sm text-text-muted">APK (arm64, sideload)</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-6 text-center text-[12px] text-text-muted">
      Τελευταία έκδοση από GitHub Releases &mdash; Auto-update ενσωματωμένο.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
